<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1013517">*这是30个妄想症开团点子，阅读它们可能会让你失去30个团。<br>*翻译自官方素材，<a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/m/product/207152" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">《30个反叛的妄想症阴谋》</a>。<br>*感谢GaRa提供资源。<br>*吐槽<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">说是开团点子，但其实有些比CODE7还详细的！</div></div></div><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>警告！警告！这可能是目前为止本分区最白的贴子了，如果您不是GM，请尽快离开这里！</strong></span><br><br><hr /><br><strong>供大家认领的目录</strong><br><br>锅的分布：<br>水明子：<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">维稳专员红</span><br>泡泡：<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">绿色</span><br>路人：<span style="color: lightskyblue;" class="bbc_color">浅天蓝色</span><br>999：<span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color">基佬紫</span><br>Ga酱：<span style="color: Darkgrey;" class="bbc_color">深灰色</span><br>旧日酱：<span style="color: magenta;" class="bbc_color">洋红色</span><br>海棠：<span style="color: blueviolet;" class="bbc_color">紫罗兰色</span><br>红豆：<span style="color: Maroon;" class="bbc_color">栗色</span><br>七夜：<span style="color: steelblue;" class="bbc_color">钢蓝色</span><br><br><hr /><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-s